{"tid":591177,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳淑莊質疑未釋除疑慮　鄭若驊堅稱一地兩檢沒違基本法","createTime":"2018-03-13T09:52:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-13T10:19:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7a9b659bd5b82a5e3ef790c23f34ccf3d32f621f","tid":591177,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T09:52:11.000Z","msg":"陳淑莊質疑未釋除疑慮　鄭若驊堅稱一地兩檢沒違基本法<br />\n<br />\n對於大律師公會的意見書指，一地兩檢條例草案沒有憲制基礎，而且違反《基本法》，又指立法會沒有權力通過違反《基本法》的法例。 律政司司長鄭若驊表示，尊重不同的意見和看法，重申一地兩檢條例草案沒有牴觸《基本法》，會盡力向議員解釋沒有違反《基本法》。 <br />\n<br />\n公民黨議員陳淑莊認為，大律師公會再次以嚴厲字眼反映對一地兩檢的意見，清楚表達對一地兩檢的看法，亦就條例草案細節提出大量質疑。 陳淑莊認為，這反映政府至今未能釋除社會上尤其是專業團體的憂慮，質疑政府加快立法進度，是罔顧《基本法》，認為政府有責任先處理憲法和政治問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1385556-20180313.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1385556-20180313.htm&d=pBSnc7Ak3Aq9zpuZKNn22sP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=0b2dddb4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1385556-20180313.htm&h=2bb8df20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1385556-20180313.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fb656c161c80b334fc3e90b099da25498e8b73cf","tid":591177,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊根本仲錄音機過上手<br />\n自己單僭建都係獨狂讀稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e344f49df5c27eb450775eef74c80ecb6a9e78ba","tid":591177,"uid":87780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb656c161c80b334fc3e90b099da25498e8b73cf","tid":591177,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-13T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"鄭若驊根本仲錄音機過上手<br />\n自己單僭建都係獨狂讀稿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norm